message.body: Not sure if you have plans to come to S. Philly. If so, I'm bartending at Beau and have your cashola.
I was planning on it around 8
Excellent! I'm on a double and it's been sloooowwww.
Warm those biscuits up, cut them in half and put some butter on them or make an egg sandwich
I broke into the biscuit bag. Couldn't wait. They're delicious! I still have 2 left and will heat em' in the morning. Thanks!!!!
They are easy to make if you want instruction
Easy for you... I'll gladly accept your baked offerings any time and will continue sending stir fries and Beau leftovers your way. I'm hungover today... too much tequila after work.
